{"id":123082,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/《自题盘腿小照》/","date":"2010-11-17T20:22:36Z","modified":"2010-11-17T20:22:36Z","title":"《自题盘腿小照》","content":"<p><p><span><br />\n《自题盘腿小照》<span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p></span></span></p>\n<p><span>落叶淡淡地飘过肩头</span></p>\n<p><span>风清清地拂过脸颊</span></p>\n<p><span>柔柔的阳光和目光中</span></p>\n<p><span>盘腿而坐气息悠悠</span></p>\n<p><span>深入秋的殿堂</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span>被老子过关时的玄想</span></p>\n<p><span>染透了外衣</span></p>\n<p><span>但不影响里面的红</span></p>\n<p><span>几千年依旧红得热烈</span></p>\n<p><span>致虚极守静笃之后</span></p>\n<p><span>乾元生气勃勃光明一片</span></p>\n<p><span>身边有石头开始柔软</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span>如果打开我的胸膛</span></p>\n<p><span>你会看到尧舜和孔孟</span></p>\n<p><span>传下来的那个</span></p>\n<p><span>春光永恒又</span></p>\n<p><span>步态如秋的</span></p>\n<p><span>中国</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010-11-10东海儒者余樟法</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n格筠摄于生态公园<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> <a href=\"http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/500a591dg94c373074143\"><img src=\"http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/500a591dg94c373074143&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<div>\n<p><a href=\"http://move.blog.sina.com.cn/admin/blogmove/blogmove_msn.php\">MSN空间完美搬家到新浪博客!</a></p>\n</div>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}